messages.text: omg I want to die X_X
oh no! don't say that! whats wrong? :(
everything! today was so terrible
and it was just a day in the life of the idiot rebecca D:
is this about what happened in history class?
oh don't even REMIND me about that
jared must think i'm the stupidest girl in the world
ur too hard on yourself, becca. everybody brain farts
history and geography is supposed to be the one thing im good at
“theres 5 continents” i SAID that in front of the whole class
you don't have to rehash it becca...
and when people snicker & i realize im an idiot, how do i try to save it?
“I MEAN 6 IF YOU COUNT ANTARTICA”
ur not an idiot, you just panic under pressure
nobody cares. everyone will have forgotten about it by monday. even jared
hold on, i think i heard something in rick's room
if my idiot brother ditched school again today and snuck back home...
lol y do u care?
y should i have to be miserable @ school & he get to skip?
ur brother isnt your problem, becca. u need to stop worrying so much
he's not home. this is really weird
r u alone?
no, moms downstairs getting ready to go to book club
she found out about the english paper i got a 0 on
woah, when did that happen? o_o
2 weeks back. i just forgot the deadline. Henderson doesn't accept late work
i'd finished it a week earlier and then just forgot about it!
oh no! D: is ur grade ok in the class ok?
it dropped to a C- & mom just chewed me out. i'm such an idiot
i just want to curl up in bed and never get up again >.<
ur not an idiot! u just make bad decisions when ur stressed out. youre your own worst enemy here
...rebecca?
theres something upstairs. someone is here
OMG r u sure its not ur brother?
i jut called him. he's on the bus home still
maybe its a mouse or something
im getting mom. i can't deal with this
becca, ur freaking me out. if u think someone is in your house, call the cops!
OMG mom “cant hear it”
its getting louder. I hear it moving
y cant she hear it!? T_T
u need to calm down rebecca
she thinks im crazy
OH NO. shes leaving for her book club. im going to be alone
BECCA. you've had a long day. ur super stressed and not in a good headspace. just chill
ur a 17-yo girl. you'll be fine home alone for the afternoon
yeah, ur right
i can't even hear it anymore. it was probably just a mouse or something. ewww :P
...i'm such an idiot
what? no! not this again... :/
i just had a total panic attack over a mouse! i cant
OMG I HEARD IT AGAIN
jen, someone is DEFINITELY downstairs now
moms gone and i hear someone getting into cupboards
becca...
hold on. im scared. im going to get rick's baseball bat
OMG I SAW HER
WHO?
she was sitting in the kitchen...
what did she look like? O:
me
she looked just like me
what r u doing now?
hiding upstairs
i think she saw me
what was she wearing?
my water polo sweatshirt and jeans
becca, u need to call the police and leave now
what if they cant hear her either?
becca, r u...are u ok?
u think im crazy too dont u?
i didn't say that. i just think u need to stay calm
HOW CAN I STAY CALM? I CAN'T DEAL WIH THAT THING DOWNSTAIRS
oh god
its coming up
like it heard me screaming at u over text
becca, the more u freak out, the worse it gets
it only moves when ur panicking
...u are totally right...
where r u?
in the laundry, hiding under the linens
ok, ur safe for now
yeah. ok. safe for now
u can do this
u can make it go away
i believe in u, rebecca
believe in urself
yeah. i am a capable, competent human being
i dont have to be scared. i dont have to be afraid
that's right!
jen, its getting closer
i think shes looking for me
but thats ok. u picked a good hiding spot. she won't find u
but what if its not good enough? :/
OMG she's in the room
don't think like that! have confidence!
even if she found u, so what?
she can't hurt u. you wouldn't hurt urself
yeah. alright
im the real me
what can she do?
exactly.
she's looking in the washing machine
she sounds really nervous and anxious
like she's freaking out that she can't find me
but ur ok. she'll give up and leave if u just stay calm
i don't know if i can stay calm
yes you can
no, u said it yourself, i don't make good decisions when i'm stressed :/
i freak out so easily :(
I worry too much. i panic
becca, stop it! she'll hear u!
i'm not saying anything
but your fear is so loud!
i can't do this jen
yes you can
i'm such a failure
SHE'S COMING
Jen!
Becca, just CALM DOWN!
...Becca?
REBECCA!
hi, jen?
omg. r u alright?
just fine
u had me so scared, what just happened to u, rebecca???
this isn't rebecca
this is her fear
